    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you say that, but it feels like i'm just a constant weight on them. everything i do is just a mistake or a mess that they have to clean up. sometimes i look at them and think they'd be so much lighter, so much happier, if they didn't have to deal with me. like, wouldn't they be better off if i just wasn't a part of their lives anymore?",
